Rules:
- inventory_changes should be an empty list unless the player clearly gains or loses an item. Use positive quantity_delta for gaining, negative for losing.
- Set scene_complete to true ONLY if this action resolves the final or climactic encounter of the scene and it makes narrative sense to move on. Most actions should NOT complete the scene.